de.feig
Class FeUsbScanSearch

java.lang.Object
  de.feig.FeUsbScanSearch

public class FeUsbScanSearch
extends java.lang.Object

Class for defining search criterias for the next scan or scan and open process.
More informations about search criterias can be found in the manual for the FEUSB.DLL.
